QuestData.Title: Stop the Siege
QuestData.Description: I hears dem! The Alliance come soon. Destroy three Alliance siege devices and come back to Murp.
QuestData.LogDescription: Lieutenant Murp in Wintergrasp Fortress wants you to destroy 3 Alliance siege machines.
QuestData.CompletionText: Have you destroyed their siege vehicles?
QuestData.RewardText: Good job. Murp wish he was there to help.
